name: Paradise Valley CSA Full box membership
description:
The Full Box consisits of 20 weeks of fresh seasonal produce, delivered to Madison , Dubuque, or Galena, see delivery points below. This 5/8 bushel box is enough vegetables and fruits to feed a large family for one week.  We do our best to fill it full with the highest quality produce on the farms.
Spring Box example : micro-greens, oyster mushrooms, head lettuce, spring onions, radishes, baby beets, fresh herbs, spring garlic, strawberries, and new potatoes
Mid Summer Box Example :Romain lettuce, Cabbage, broccoli, garlic, potatoes, onions, tomatoes, peppers, turnips, fennel
Fall Box Example : Celery, assorted squash, sweet corn, berries, beets, rutabega, onions, potatoes, sweet potatoes, tomatoes.
This just an example and every week it changes depending on what is available at the farm

CSA Delivery points : In Madison at 55 Oaks Corporate Center, 700 Rayovac Dr on tuesdays from 3-6pm

In Dubuque at Fountain Park Farmers market at Asbury Rd from 3-6 Pm Thursdays

In Galena at Vintalogie 225 S.Main St on Saturdays from 12-3

name: Full Box with returning customer discount only
